me.normanmaurer.niosmtp.delivery

Interface SMTPDeliverySessionConstants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAuthResponseListener, AbstractPipeliningResponseListener, AuthLoginResponseListener, AuthPlainResponseListener, ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener, DataResponseListener, EhloResponseListener, HeloResponseListener, LMTPDeliveryAgent, LMTPPostDataResponseCallback, LMTPWelcomeResponseListener, MailResponseListener, PostDataResponseListener, RcptResponseListener, SMTPDeliveryAgent, SMTPDisconnectHandler, StartTlsResponseListener, WelcomeResponseListener

    public interface SMTPDeliverySessionConstants
    Constants for temporary data which will get stored via the SMTPClientSession.setAttribute(String, Object)() while sending the message. These can then be accessed via SMTPClientSession.getAttribute(String).
    Author:
    Norman Maurer

        static final String SMTP_TRANSACTION_ACTIVE_KEY
